The user should be able to acess data such as temperature, pressure, sunshine, raifall, wind speed and wind direction every hour.
Changes in data should be timely monitored and updated in the system.
The system should monitor all the insturemnts used(health and condition).
The system should report faults if any occur.
The system should shutdown if there is potentially damaging weather.
The system should allow for dynamic redonfiguration for updates.(new version)
The backup generator should be on if there is a loss of electricity and immediately backup data.
